# {{PROJECT_NAME}} 🚀

> Modern Electron desktop application with complete user management, authentication system, and FBCA architecture

A cross-platform desktop application built with Electron, featuring a complete user authentication and management system, Feature-Based Component Architecture on both frontend and backend, comprehensive UI components from UIKit, and powerful backend modules from AppKit.

